data.description: Welcome to your future home, nestled on a fantastic corner lot boasting over 11,000 square feet of space! This charming one-story residence offers 1,828 square feet of comfortable living space, perfectly designed for modern convenience and relaxation. Step inside through the inviting double doors and be greeted by vaulted ceilings that bathe the interior in natural light, creating an airy and welcoming ambiance. The focal point of the living area is a cozy wood-burning fireplace, ideal for gathering with loved ones on chilly evenings. With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, including an oversized primary bedroom featuring an ample walk-in closet, this home offers plenty of space and comfort for the entire family. The indoor laundry adds to the convenience of everyday living. Experience indoor-outdoor living at its finest with both an enclosed patio and a new covered patio, providing the perfect spaces for entertaining guests or simply relaxing outdoors. Recent upgrades enhance the home's appeal, including a new gas water heater, garage door opener, light fixtures, blinds throughout, a new Nest thermostat, and a central vacuum system. For those with recreational vehicles or additional storage needs, the gated RV access ensures plenty of space to accommodate your vehicles and toys. Furthermore, this property presents an exceptional opportunity for financing options. It qualifies for 100% financing, offering flexibility for buyers. Additionally, it is eligible for a VA loan assumption at an attractive low interest rate of 4.625%, providing further financial advantages for qualified buyers. Low Solar payment! Don't miss out on the chance to make this fantastic property your own! Schedule a viewing today and envision the possibilities of calling this place home.
